column5: I have not posted on this forum in a long time - mainly due to a lack of fishing opportunities  Managed to sneak out for a night time fish in the Kawarthas this weekend  2 walleye caught - one about 19 inches and the other just shy of 18  - both in the slot, both caught trolling the outside weed edge  Hoping to get out a few more times at the cottage and I am lucky to have two fly in trips planned this summer  Cheers Gordy
Better late than never right? Nice fish and good luck on your fly ins!
